Tyrael: Ah! Shadow Star! There you are! Help me bring the main power 
back up. Talon, try to check for some planets in this area.

The phoenix went to a compartment on the left side of the bridge and 
opened it. He pulled lever out of it which brought the power generator 
back online.

Tyrael: Now, lieutenant, get on the computer and reassign power to all 
the ship. And where is Naga?
